text: Bous-Waldbredimus is a commune in southeastern Luxembourg. It is part of the canton of Remich. It was created on 1 September 2023 from the former communes of Bous and Waldbredimus. As of 2023, 1,752 people live here. Category:2023 establishments in Europe Category:21st-century establishments in Luxembourg Category:Communes of Remich
title: Bous-Waldbredimus
